"The saturation of the image, so that 0 means no saturation and 2 means "
"infinite saturation."
msgstr ""

#: src/effects/effects.js:264
msgid "Pixelize"
msgstr ""

#: src/effects/effects.js:265
msgid "An effect that pixelizes the image."
